**Device:** Tuya PJ-1203A - Bidirectional Energy Meter with 2x 80A CT Clamps
**Purchase Link**: https://es.aliexpress.com/item/1005007427346306.html
**Model:** TS0601
**Manufacturer:** _TZE204_81yrt3lo
**Protocol:** Zigbee

**Description:**
Dual channel bidirectional energy meter with 80A current clamp sensors.
The device pairs successfully with Homey Pro but CT clamp sensor data 
(power_a, power_b, current_a, current_b, voltage, energy) is not reported.

**Zigbee2MQTT reference (device is fully supported there):**
https://www.zigbee2mqtt.io/devices/PJ-1203A.html

**Expected capabilities:**
- measure_power (channel A and B)
- measure_current (channel A and B)  
- measure_voltage
- meter_power (energy kWh, channel A and B)
- energy_flow direction (consuming/producing)

**Note:** Similar variant _TZE284_81yrt3lo was fixed in v5.7.7. 
This is the _TZE204_ variant which still has no sensor data.






